# Awesome Global Girls Project Structure

This is an Astro-based project showcasing inspiring women from around the world for Hacktoberfest 2025.

## Key Files

- [src/pages/index.astro](mdc:src/pages/index.astro) - Main page with search functionality
- [src/data/girls.json](mdc:src/data/girls.json) - JSON data file containing women's information
- [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) - Global styles
- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Astro configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration

## Project Features

- **Search Functionality**: Real-time search across name, country, and field
- **Responsive Design**: Uses DaisyUI components with Tailwind CSS
- **Data-driven**: Content is loaded from JSON file
- **Accessibility**: Proper semantic HTML and ARIA attributes

## Data Structure

Each entry in [src/data/girls.json](mdc:src/data/girls.json) should have:

- `name`: Full name of the person
- `country`: Country of origin
- `field`: Professional field/industry
- `href`: Wikipedia or reference link
- `image`: Path to image file (optional)

## Styling Guidelines

- Use DaisyUI components for consistency
- Follow the existing purple gradient theme
- Maintain responsive grid layout
- Use proper semantic HTML structure
